const AboutHeroImage = "/me.png";
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	description="Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet"
	pubDate={new Date('May 25 2026')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		Gamze Yıldız is a Civil Engineering graduate of Gazi University, where she developed a strong
		foundation in structural engineering and coastal engineering. She is currently pursuing her 
		Master's degree in Civil Engineering Department at Middle East Technical University (METU).
		Her research interests focus on the seismic performance of pile-supported offshore structures,
		with particular emphasis on nonlinear soil-structure interaction (SSI) and numerical modeling 
		techniques in structural engineering.

	</p>

	<p>
		She is currently working as a Civil Engineer in a private engineering company, where she 
		contributes to the design development and technical documentation of military and commercial 
		airport projects as a part of multidisciplinary and international teams.
	</p>

	<p>
		She has experience with a range of engineering software and computational tools used in 
		structural and hydraulic engineering applications, including SAP2000, OpenSees, XTRACT, 
		AutoCAD, HEC-RAS, Civil 3D, and MATLAB, as well as standard MS Office tools for engineering 
		documentation and reporting.
	</p>

	<p>
		She has an advanced level of proficiency in English, which supports her academic and 
		professional communication in engineering contexts. She has an intermediate level of 
		French and is enthusiastic about further improving her language skills.

</Layout>
